tric and adolescent health outcomes and empowering and educating parents. June 2025 - Journal Impact Factor 2.3. Q2 journal in Pediatrics category. (Source: Journal Citation Reports™ 2025 from Clarivate™) ",description:b,path:bp,slug:bp,seq:y,enabled:c,environment:d,url:"https:\u002F\u002Fpediatrics.jmir.org",batch:e,year:x,colour:"#d2a9ad",impact:bq,order:B,published:556,transfers:a,cite_score:"4.5"},{journal_id:m,title:"Interactive Journal of Medical Research",tag:"A new general medical journal for the 21st centrury, focusing on innovation in health and medical research. June 2025 - Journal Impact Factor 2.2. (Source: Journal Citation Reports™ 2025 from Clarivate™) ",description:b,path:"ijmr",slug:"i-jmr",seq:p,enabled:c,environment:d,url:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.i-jmr.org",batch:e,year:Z,colour:"#22B2C1",impact:af,order:E,published:548,transfers:a,cite_score:a},{journal_id:p,title:"iProceedings",tag:"Electronic Proceedings, Presentations and Posters of Leading Conferences",description:b,path:br,slug:br,seq:B,enabled:c,environment:d,url:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.iproc.org",batch:e,year:w,colour:"#6F7D80",impact:a,order:aa,published:510,transfers:a,cite_score:a},{journal_id:E,title:"JMIR Rehabilitation and Assistive Technologies",tag:"Development and Evaluation of Rehabilitation, Physiotherapy and Assistive Technologies, Robotics, Prosthetics and Implants, Mobility and Communication Tools, Home Automation and Telerehabilitation. June 2025 - Journal Impact Factor 3.0. (Source: Journal Citation Reports™ 2025 from Clarivate™) ",description:b,path:bs,slug:bs,seq:R,enabled:c,environment:d,url:"https:\u002F\u002Frehab.jmir.org",batch:e,year:$,colour:"#15638E",impact:bh,order:C,published:bt,transfers:a,cite_score:"5.7"},{journal_id:y,title:"JMIR Dermatology",tag:"Technologies, devices, apps, and informatics applications for patient education in dermatology, including preventative interventions, and clinical care for dermatological populations",description:b,path:bu,slug:bu,seq